    <li>Improve performance (throughput and loss rate) for PPTP, <a href="http://man.openbsd.org?query=pppd&manpath=OpenBSD%20Current&sektion=8&format=html">pppd(8)</a> or L2TP(/IPsec) on unstable latency networks (eg mobile).
